                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-12-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">用大白话把佛学讲的很透，好熊真好！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
