    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1200083785">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1200083785" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1200083785" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1200083785">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hayeke2325156/">绛枫</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">《六祖坛经》的现代文翻译和解说本，对佛学不了解的读者或有裨益。但禅宗并非只有坛经，佛学更是体系庞杂，包罗万象，此书仅涉皮毛。另外，对于唯识学“阿赖耶识”的解释过于简略且有失偏颇。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1191982674">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1191982674" class="vote-count">0</span>
